    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbortedResponse

    public abstract class FinalizedClientResponse
extends ClientResponse
    A class that adds a Object#finalize) method to the {@link ClientResponse} as a last ditch backstop to prevent leaking resources with ill-behaved clients. Use of finalize could incur a significant performance penalty.
